274
00:15:28,814 --> 00:15:30,405
Itu mudah bagi kami.

275
00:15:30,405 --> 00:15:31,346
Bagus.

276
00:15:31,793 --> 00:15:32,878
Benimaru.

277
00:15:33,325 --> 00:15:38,021
Saya tak ragu-ragu pada awak tapi awak akan berdepan dengan 100 askar berkuda.

278
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,572
Jadi, saya...

279
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:41,116
Jangan risau.

280
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:43,746
Sebab kita dah kesuntukan masa ni.

281
00:15:44,511 --> 00:15:47,572
Kalau begitu, kau tak perlu risau apa-apa lagi.

282
00:15:48,003 --> 00:15:52,163
Rimuru-sama, aku nak ingatkan kau semula lagi tentang perkara tu.

283
00:15:52,340 --> 00:15:56,239
Dengan kau meletakkan aku di Barat, itu bermakna...

284
00:16:01,076 --> 00:16:03,821
