304
00:16:55,230 --> 00:16:56,245
Baik!

305
00:16:56,897 --> 00:16:57,774
Shuna.

306
00:16:58,030 --> 00:16:58,667
Ya.

307
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:01,228
