309
00:17:04,600 --> 00:17:05,770
Awak faham maksud saya, kan?

310
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:06,757
Ya.

311
00:17:07,070 --> 00:17:09,612
Saya perlu buat satu penghadang lain, kan?

312
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:11,239
